item.title: About
item.description: I am a bioinformatician in the process of converting into a data scientist. Totally nerdy about data visualization, and studying data trends. Also a foodie, climber, and yogi. Using the coronavirus quarantine period to teach myself to make a website, visualize coronavirus data, and machine learning / AI stuff.
